title: Recap of Seahawks' crucial MNF win, Bruce Feldman talks college coaches and QBs
itunes:title: Recap of Seahawks' crucial MNF win, Bruce Feldman talks college coaches and QBs
description:
DJ and Bucky are back with a new episode. First, the guys recap the Seahawks' Monday Night Football win against the Vikings, as they give their takeaways from that game (3:00). Next, the duo look at if the Bengals should go quarterback or pass rusher in the 2020 NFL Draft, if the team gets the top pick (14:16). After, the pair talk with college football reporter and writer Bruce Feldman, as he discusses the latest news on college football coaches and talks about a few of the top college quarterbacks in the country (22:20).
